{
  "chapterIndex": 3,
  "pageIndex": 12,
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "They walked back toward the trolley as the light began to fade."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "The city softened again."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Edges blurring."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Colors warming."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Everything slowing down just enough to feel it."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "They reached the corner where the trolley would come."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Stopped."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Not because they had to."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Because neither of them moved first."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Ethan glanced at her."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Then—without overthinking it this time—"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "he reached out."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Took her hand."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Gently."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "No hesitation."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "No pretending it was accidental."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Cassandra looked down at their hands."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Then back up at him."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Her fingers tightened slightly around his."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "She didn’t pull away."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Didn’t question it."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Didn’t make it smaller than it was."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Which made it bigger."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "The trolley arrived."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Neither of them let go right away."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Even as they stepped on."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Even as they sat down again."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Even as the city moved around them."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Later that night—"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Cassandra sat on her bed again."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Phone in hand."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Harold beside her."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Her fingers hovered over the screen."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Then typed:"
    },
    {
      "type": "textMessage",
      "messages": [
        { "sender": "Cassandra", "content": "I think this is going to hurt." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "She stared at it."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Read it twice."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Then—"
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "deleted it."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Replaced it with:"
    },
    {
      "type": "textMessage",
      "messages": [
        { "sender": "Cassandra", "content": "Today was really good." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "She set the phone down."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Her chest tightened again."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Not the same way."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Never the same way."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "This one stayed longer."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "She lay back slowly, staring at the ceiling."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "I shouldn’t do this."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "The thought came clearly."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Honest."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Unavoidable."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "Her fingers curled slightly into the blanket."
    },
    {
      "type": "narration",
      "content": "So why does it feel like the only thing I want?"
    }
  ]
}